1944;;One Exciting Night;;British;;Walter Forde;;Vera Lynn, Donald Stewart;;musical;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/One_Exciting_Night_(1944_film);;Vera Baker is an aspiring singer desperate for an opportunity to impress producer Michael Thorne. Her chance arrives at a benefit concert that is also the scene of an attempted kidnapping of Thorne by gangsters chasing a priceless Rembrandt. Vera somehow eventually thwarts the villains, and along the way manages to wow the audience with her singing.